{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "main_16", "eventName": "反常光譜", "entryType": "MAINLINE", "storyCode": "EG-9", "avgTag": "幕間", "storyName": "歸鄉", "storyInfo": "等炮火止歇、痛呼沉寂，我要回到我母親的身旁，就像出生時那樣。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "50_g13_warshipcommandroom", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$darkness01_intro", "key": "$darkness01_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_telegraph_loop", "loop": "true", "channel": "bgs"}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“各單位注意，這裡是調度中心。”"}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“根據聖駿堡緊急電報要求，各單位立即停火。”"}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“重複，各單位立即停火。”"}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“收到請回覆。”"}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1977_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呼……", "name": "軍官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1977_1#1$1"}, {"id": 20, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "停火範圍？", "name": "軍官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1977_1#1$1"}, {"id": 21, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所有出戰單位。", "name": "通訊兵"}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1977_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（點頭）", "name": "軍官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1977_1#1$1"}, {"id": 25, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“收到。”"}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1977_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "通知伊爾欽中尉，儘快確認第二師下轄所有兵團是否停火。", "name": "軍官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1977_1#1$1"}, {"id": 29, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“各單位原地待命，保持戰鬥警戒。”"}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“在徹底清除威脅之前，我們將繼續踐行拱衛聖駿堡、保護人民的誓言。”"}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$p_imp_funnel_end_h"}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "bgs", "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1977_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……去叫軍需官過來。", "name": "軍官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1977_1#1$1"}, {"id": 38, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1976_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "報告長官，這次我們沒有軍需官隨軍行動。", "name": "士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1976_1#1$1"}, {"id": 40, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您預期這只是一次快速反應行動——把那些製造暴亂的感染者都消滅不會花費太多的時間。", "name": "士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1976_1#1$1"}, {"id": 41, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1977_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "軍官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1977_1#1$1"}, {"id": 43, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "士兵，先照常回覆調度中心。", "name": "軍官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1977_1#1$1"}, {"id": 44, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "然後，你叫什麼名字？", "name": "軍官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1977_1#1$1"}, {"id": 45, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1976_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "報告長官，我是列兵維亞切·季諾夫。", "name": "士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1976_1#1$1"}, {"id": 47, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1977_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好，列兵維亞切，去通知中尉吧，這裡暫時不需要你的服務了。", "name": "軍官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1977_1#1$1"}, {"id": 49, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_warehouse_2", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1978_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……就這麼一件小事，值得讓我擅離職守過來找你？", "name": "冷漠的士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1978_1#1$1"}, {"id": 59, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我看你是瘋了。", "name": "冷漠的士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1978_1#1$1"}, {"id": 60, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1976_1#1$1", "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "帕季亞，你看你穿著盾衛的制服，多麼威風……！", "name": "憤怒的士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1976_1#1$1"}, {"id": 65, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "戴著那頂頭盔難道真的讓你什麼都看不見了嗎？", "name": "憤怒的士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1976_1#1$1"}, {"id": 66, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那些軍糧裡的蛆蟲、一折就斷的弩箭——甚至還有啞彈！", "name": "憤怒的士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1976_1#1$1"}, {"id": 67, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們就用這種東西出去送死！", "name": "憤怒的士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1976_1#1$1"}, {"id": 68, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1978_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 69, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "軍糧裡面有蟲，那就吃有蟲的軍糧；武器難以使用，那就用身體去戰鬥。", "name": "冷漠的士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1978_1#1$1"}, {"id": 70, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們是士兵，我們戰鬥，然後勝利。結局只有繼續戰鬥或死去。", "name": "冷漠的士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1978_1#1$1"}, {"id": 71, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1976_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 72, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我看你才是瘋了！", "name": "憤怒的士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1976_1#1$1"}, {"id": 73, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1978_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "發現他人職責上的失誤，你應該報告給上級，而不是在這裡向我抱怨。", "name": "冷漠的士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1978_1#1$1"}, {"id": 75, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我不是軍需官——", "name": "冷漠的士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1978_1#1$1"}, {"id": 76, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 77, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 78, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_armyboots_walk", "loop": "true", "channel": "bgs"}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1977_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 80, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "bgs", "fadetime": 0.3}}, {"id": 82, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我記得重裝兵團應該在甲板上駐守。", "name": "軍官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1977_1#1$1"}, {"id": 84, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1978_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……抱歉長官，我的確擅離職守了。", "name": "冷漠的士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1978_1#1$1"}, {"id": 86, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我會將此失職行為上報給督戰官。", "name": "冷漠的士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1978_1#1$1"}, {"id": 87, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（敬禮）", "name": "冷漠的士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1978_1#1$1"}, {"id": 88, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_armour"}}, {"id": 90, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 92, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1977_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 94, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "軍官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1977_1#1$1"}, {"id": 95, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1976_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 96, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "長官！", "name": "憤怒的士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1976_1#1$1"}, {"id": 97, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1977_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 98, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "士兵，你發現了什麼？", "name": "軍官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1977_1#1$1"}, {"id": 99, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "告訴我使你憤怒的緣由。", "name": "軍官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1977_1#1$1"}, {"id": 100, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1976_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……這次行動，我們軍需用品的品質非常低劣。", "name": "憤怒的士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1976_1#1$1"}, {"id": 102, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "軍糧偷工減料，配給的罐頭全都破損，裡面長滿了蛆蟲……", "name": "憤怒的士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1976_1#1$1"}, {"id": 103, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還有弩箭……箭頭有不少都不是鋼製的，而是用生鐵濫竽充數。", "name": "憤怒的士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1976_1#1$1"}, {"id": 104, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "甚至備用的源石炸彈含有的能量極低，幾乎和啞彈沒有區別。", "name": "憤怒的士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1976_1#1$1"}, {"id": 105, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就這樣……這樣要我們怎麼進行下一步行動？", "name": "憤怒的士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1976_1#1$1"}, {"id": 106, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1977_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……士兵，你是為了什麼而從軍的？", "name": "軍官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1977_1#1$1"}, {"id": 108, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1976_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 109, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "為……", "name": "憤怒的士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1976_1#1$1"}, {"id": 110, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1977_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "大聲回答我。", "name": "軍官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1977_1#1$1"}, {"id": 112, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1976_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "為——為了證明自己！我想讓自己的名字被更多人知道——", "name": "憤怒的士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1976_1#1$1"}, {"id": 114, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "像您一樣！", "name": "憤怒的士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1976_1#1$1"}, {"id": 115, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1977_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當軍隊送回你的軍牌，你的母親把你的名字刻在白樺樹上，同樣是一種眾人皆知。", "name": "軍官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1977_1#1$1"}, {"id": 117, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1976_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 118, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，不是那種……", "name": "憤怒的士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1976_1#1$1"}, {"id": 119, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1977_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 120, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果集體已經身處一場戰爭，那個人就不會有太多選擇自己結局的餘地。", "name": "軍官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1977_1#1$1"}, {"id": 121, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但……", "name": "軍官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1977_1#1$1"}, {"id": 122, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "保持這種希望吧，孩子，然後把你的“發現”記在心裡。", "name": "軍官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1977_1#1$1"}, {"id": 123, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "為了讓更多的烏薩斯人能夠活下去，為了烏薩斯的存續，事到如今，留給我們的選擇只有一個了……", "name": "軍官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1977_1#1$1"}, {"id": 124, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 125, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 127, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "用一把火點燃這片大地。", "name": "軍官"}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 129, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 131, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "hidecgitem", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}